I'm here

00:40:13.760 --> 00:40:16.240
to tell you something sincere.

00:40:16.960 --> 00:40:17.840
Go ahead.

00:40:19.080 --> 00:40:21.760
I'm very happy

00:40:23.000 --> 00:40:24.560
I'm very happy.

00:40:25.800 --> 00:40:26.840
You've grown up.

00:40:28.120 --> 00:40:29.840
You're a man now.

00:40:30.440 --> 00:40:32.680
You will be successful in the future.

00:40:34.720 --> 00:40:36.760
But I have to remind you.

00:40:38.000 --> 00:40:40.640
No matter who you meet in the future,

00:40:40.960 --> 00:40:42.800
no matter what they ask you,

00:40:43.040 --> 00:40:44.960
you have to pretend that you don't know anything.

00:40:45.200 --> 00:40:46.800
All you do is study.

00:40:48.360 --> 00:40:49.600
Got it?

00:40:50.360 --> 00:40:51.280
Father.

00:40:51.760 --> 00:40:53.120
Why did you say that?

00:40:53.480 --> 00:40:54.560
To live.

00:40:54.920 --> 00:40:58.240
Don't you feel suffocated living like this?

00:41:00.400 --> 00:41:01.480
No.

00:41:02.960 --> 00:41:06.040
You'll feel sad if you can't live.

00:41:06.760 --> 00:41:07.880
Father.

00:41:08.240 --> 00:41:09.680
I don't want to live a miserable life.

00:41:15.720 --> 00:41:16.800
Good son.

00:41:17.360 --> 00:41:19.200
No matter how hard it is,

00:41:19.400 --> 00:41:20.280
no matter how hard it is,

00:41:21.000 --> 00:41:22.800
I'll bear it for you.

00:41:23.000 --> 00:41:25.400
I only pray to God

00:41:25.600 --> 00:41:28.560
to be safe.

00:41:29.720 --> 00:41:31.480
Remember

00:41:31.960 --> 00:41:33.280
what I just told you.

00:41:39.560 --> 00:41:40.680
Okay.

00:41:40.880 --> 00:41:41.800
Read your book.

00:41:42.640 --> 00:41:43.800
I'm going back.

00:41:59.600 --> 00:42:00.960
So there's no

00:42:01.080 --> 00:42:02.360
Japanese will attack.

00:42:02.720 --> 00:42:04.600
There's no sniper battle you mentioned.

00:42:06.520 --> 00:42:08.320
Why don't they attack

00:42:08.520 --> 00:42:09.680
and attack?

00:42:09.880 --> 00:42:10.760
I don't know.

00:42:10.960 --> 00:42:12.400
But I can't tell you

00:42:12.600 --> 00:42:13.640
I can't tell you.

00:42:15.760 --> 00:42:16.840
Next,

00:42:17.920 --> 00:42:20.280
we are waiting for the Japanese to attack.

00:42:21.720 --> 00:42:23.960
The situation on the battlefield is changing rapidly.

00:42:24.560 --> 00:42:27.000
It's just a matter of timing.

00:42:28.560 --> 00:42:29.480
Okay.

00:42:30.520 --> 00:42:32.440
It seems that no matter what the situation is,

00:42:33.120 --> 00:42:34.240
As a reporter,

00:42:34.680 --> 00:42:36.080
I can only wait.

00:42:38.200 --> 00:42:38.880
Captain Joo.

00:42:38.960 --> 00:42:39.560
Yes.

00:42:42.160 --> 00:42:43.280
Contact Wu Zhen for me.

00:42:43.440 --> 00:42:44.320
Tell him I need to talk to him.

00:42:44.400 --> 00:42:45.000
Yes.

00:42:46.200 --> 00:42:47.200
Wu Zhen.

00:42:48.880 --> 00:42:51.000
You asked me if I was a commie.

00:42:51.200 --> 00:42:51.840
Yes.

